dict.string: tell application "System Events" tell process "PDF Expert" set frontmost to true click menu item "Annotation Summary" of menu "View" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell
tell application "System Events" tell process "PDF Expert" set frontmost to true click menu item "Remove All Annotations" of menu "Edit" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell
tell application "System Events" tell process "PDF Expert" set frontmost to true click menu item "Note" of menu "Annotate" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell

tell application "System Events" to set frontApp to (name of first process where it is frontmost)
if (frontApp = "PDF Expert) then tell application "System Events" tell process "PDF Expert" to click menu item "Day" of menu of menu item "Theme" of menu "View" of menu bar 1 end tell end if
tell application "System Events" tell process "Highlights" set frontmost to true click menu item "Night" of menu of menu item "PDF Appearance" of menu "View" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell
tell application "System Events" tell process "Highlights" set frontmost to true click menu item "Rename…" of menu "File" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell
tell application "System Events" tell process "Microsoft Word" set frontmost to true click menu item "Comment" of menu "Insert" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell
tell application "System Events" set frontApp to (name of first process where it is frontmost) tell process frontApp to click menu item "Export..." of menu "File" of menu bar 1 end tell
tell application "System Events" tell process "Microsoft Word" to click menu item "Save As..." of menu "File" of menu bar 1 end tell
